n UFOs released (mostly through Freedom of Information Act suits) over the past few years by the Departments of State / Army / Navy /Air Force/Defense, the Federal Bureau of Investigation, the National Securitv Agency, the Detense Intelligence Agency and the central Intelligence Agency.|access-date=2021-08-18|archive-date=2021-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709171322/https://www.nsa.gov/Portals/70/documents/news-features/declassified-documents/ufo/what_gov_knows_about_ufos.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=UFO Documents Index|url=https://www.nsa.gov/news-features/declassified-documents/ufo/|publisher=NSA|access-date=2021-08-18|archive-date=2021-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210823211816/https://www.nsa.gov/news-features/declassified-documents/ufo/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=What Do NSA and NASA Have in Common?|url=https://www.nsa.gov/News-Features/Feature-Stories/Article-View/Article/2710684/what-do-nsa-and-nasa-have-in-common/|publisher=NSA|access-date=2021-08-18|archive-date=2021-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210813000133/https://www.nsa.gov/News-Features/Feature-Stories/Article-View/Article/2710684/what-do-nsa-and-nasa-have-in-common/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==背景==
雖然有許多飛碟學家努力爭取科學界的認同，但是即使有一些具有名望的學者，例如[[約瑟夫·艾倫·海尼克|約瑟夫·艾倫·海尼克]]、[[詹姆斯·麥當勞|詹姆斯·麥當勞]]、[[雅克‧瓦萊|雅克‧瓦萊]]（Jacques Vallee）、[[彼得·斯迪羅克|彼得·斯迪羅克]]（Peter Sturrock）等，參與研究，飛碟學仍然不被主流科學界認為是一門科學。

